eNCA's Moloko Moloto reports. Courtesy #DStv403 JOHANNESBURG - Nursing union Denosa is threatening mass demonstrations against the Gauteng government. READ: Denosa calls for better protection for healthcare workers This is over the non-payment of salaries for community services nurses and the retrenchments of some of its members. The union is calling for the provincial health department to prioritise nurses. Watch the video above for more details. 